channel.title: Need help with my Project Insanity base
channel.description:
I'm using a Projet insanity base, [Lost legacy to be exact] I'm trying to open a shop, a donator shop. I have the shop spawned in the spawn-config, I have the shop in npc2.py, I have the shop in the shops.cfg file, and the npc is showing up and everything, its just when I click trade, the trade window is not popping up. Is there something I'm missing?
Help please? :D
